User Rights Assignment
Deny access to computer from the network
Deny log on through Remote Desktop Services

Type this in User and group names in the Security Policy Setting
    Local account and member of Administrators group

In one or more GPOs that you create and link to workstation and member server OUs in each domain, add the Administrator account to the following 
user rights in Computer Configuration\Policies\Windows Settings\Security Settings\Local Policies\User Rights Assignments:

Deny access to this computer from the network
Deny log on as a batch job
Deny log on as a service
Deny log on through Remote Desktop Services

